Rd1 Rfd8 (29... d3 $2 30. Na3 {[%cal Yb4b5]}) 30. Be4 d3 31. Na3 {[%cal Yb4b5]
White has b4-b5 and the passed pawn is lost.} Rb8 32. b5 Bxb5 33. Nxb5 Rxb5 34.
Rxd3 Rdb8 35. Rc3 g6 $11) 27... Nc5 $1 {[%cal Yc5d3,Yc5b7] Black has
