Nfd7 $1 9. Be3 Nc6 10. O-O O-O 11. f4 {This looks like an ambitious move, but
Black has a simple operation to neutralize White's plans.} Nxd4 12. Qxd4 (12.
Bxd4 {allows} b5 $1 {when} 13. e5 $6 {can be met by} dxe5 $1 14. fxe5 (14. Bxa8
