17. Bxe5 (17. Bg3 $2 Nc4 $36 {[%cal Yf8e8,Gg5f6,Gc4e3] ;Haring,F (2155)
-Firouzja,A (2481)/World ol U16 2016 (1.2)/0-1}) 17... Re8 $1 18. h4 Rxe5 19.
