{[%cal Yf5f4]}) 37... Re8 38. Qe3 Rxf2 (38... Ree5 {[%cal Yf5f2,Ge5f5] seems
even simpler.}) 39. Qxf2 Qc3 40. Re3 Qd4 $1 {White is in zugzwang.} 41. Re1 (
41. Kh2 Qxe3 $19) (41. a4 Rf8 $19 42. Rf3 Qa1+) 41... e3 42. Qf3 e2+ 43. Kh2
Rf8 {Despite some mistakes by White, this is a model game in which Sasikiran
