is equal, but Black ended doing his usual magic and won.}) 10... Nxd4 11. Bxd4
O-O 12. O-O b5 $1 {Further preparatory moves are not necessary for Black in
this position.} 13. e5 d5 (13... dxe5 $5 {seems very promising and deserves
attention.}) 14. Qe3 $1 {[%csl Ye2] , vacating e2 for the knight.} (14. f4 $6
b4 15. Na4 a5 {[%cal Yc8a6] Black's play develops very easily now.} 16. Qe3 Ba6
17. Rf2 {Mayorga,N (2330)-Perez Ponsa,F (2467) Buenos Aires Grafica Yael-A 2nd
