initiative on the queenside, since} 21. f5 $2 Bh4 22. Rd2 h6 $1 {isn't
anything for White.}) (14. a3 Qc7 15. f4 Bc5 $5 16. Qe3 Bxd4 17. Qxd4 Bb7 18.
