20. Kxf1 Nb8 $1 {[%cal Yb8c6]}) 19... Rxc1+ 20. Rxc1 Qb8 $1 {[%cal Yf8c8]
Black is fine.}) (9. Nce2 $5 {[%cal Yc2c3,Ge2g3,Gd4f3,Yf2f4] This is an
