16. Nxb5 Nfxe4 $11) (7. f4 {This transposes to the 6.f4 variation.} Bg7 8. Nf3
Qb6 $5 {This idea is recommended by Pavlovic. White needs to solve the problem
of castling now.} 9. Qe2 O-O 10. Rb1 {The most natural solution for White.} (
10. Qf2 {Exchanging queens is usually good for Black in the Sicilian.} Qxf2+
11. Kxf2 b5 12. Re1 Bb7 13. h3 {Gdanski,J (2535)-Wahls,M (2579) Bundesliga
