Bg4 12. h3 Bxf3 13. Qxf3 Nd7 $13 {Guliev,L (2389)-Idani,P (2496) Fajr op 23rd
2015 (6) 0-1 The position offers chances for both sides, for example} 14. h4
Rac8 15. h5 $2 Nb4 $1 $132 {[%csl Ya2][%cal Yc8c1,Gg7a1]}) 10... Nc6 11. Be3
Qa5 12. O-O Bg4 13. h3 Bxf3 14. Qxf3 Nd7 15. Bd2 Rac8 16. g4 $6 (16. Kh1 $142
b5 17. a3 Qd8 18. g4 e6 $13) 16... Nc5 $132 {Patterson,R (2107)-Nakamura,H 
