[%cal Yd6d5] Black is able to make the d5-advance, with a nice position, since}
18. Bg5 $2 {is bad due to} Ng4 $1 19. fxg4 Bxg5 20. gxh5 Qxb2 $14) 10... Rc8
11. O-O (11. a5 {This should transpose after} Be7 12. O-O O-O) 11... Be7 12.
