{[#] Black should find his way in the arising complications. What is the most
precise continuation?} 12... Bb7 13. exf6 $1 Nxf6 $1 (13... Bxf3 $2 14. fxg7
Rg8 15. Bxf3 $16) 14. Qg3 b4 $1 {This is the point: Instead of regaining the
material, Black wants to take the initiative.} 15. Nb1 (15. Na4 Bxh1 16. Rxh1
e5 17. Nb3 Rc8 18. Bd1 Qc6 $1 {[%csl Ra4,Rh1] is an important tactical finesse.
} 19. Nb6 Rb8 $17) 15... Ne4 16. Qh2 {[%csl Gb1,Rc1,Gh2] White's pieces look
very awkward and Black is able to build annoying pressure against the king.}
Rc8 17. Bd3 Nc5 $1 $40 {Black had promising attacking chances in Delgado
Ramirez,N (2615)-Mareco,S (2599) Barreirinhas Athenas op 2015 (6) 0-1.} *

